ng through, making it easier for them to understand and really help their loved one. <br \/>&nbsp;<\/br>\n<li> <a href=\"\/relapse-prevention-utah\/\" title=\"Addiction Relapse Prevention - Pathways Real Life Recovery - Day Treatment Program in Utah\">Relapse Prevention<\/a>: Towards the end of treatment, a trained addiction specialist will work with you to help you become aware of your own relapse triggers and create new relapse prevention skills.<br \/>&nbsp;<\/br>\n<\/ul>\n<h3>Contact Pathways\u2019 Day Treatment Center in Utah and Start Your Path to Healing<\/h3>\n<p>Pathways Real Life Recovery\u2019s day treatment program aims to improve mental health with a holistic, evidence-based treatment methodology. We work to build up self-esteem, teach the skills needed for success, and dig deep to treat underlying issues that cause the unwanted symptomology in the first place. See how Pathways can help you overcome your addictive or other limiting behaviors to manifest positive life changes.<br \/>&nbsp;<\/br><\/p>\n<h4>Call <a href=\"tel:18018953006\" title=\"Call Pathways Real Life Recovery today to start your path to healing - Day Treatment Programs in Utah\">(801) 895-3006<\/a> to Receive a Free Consultation.<\/h4>\n<\/p><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/section><style><\/style><script type=\"text\/javascript\"><\/script>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v16.8 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Day Treatment Program in Utah - Drug Addiction, Alcoholism &amp; Mental Health<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"Looking for a day treatment program for addiction or mental disorders in Utah? Pathways Real Life Recovery - Daytime Treatment Program in Utah\" \/>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet: